sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions
    participant CLI as chrome-webstore-upload-cli
    participant OAuth as Google OAuth
    participant CWS as Chrome Web Store

    Dev->>GH: Create release (tag: beta-v1.0.1)
    GH->>GHA: Trigger publish-beta workflow

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over GHA: Build Job
        GHA->>GHA: Checkout code
        GHA->>GHA: Verify tag version matches .env version
        alt Version mismatch
            GHA-->>Dev: ❌ Workflow fails
        end
        GHA->>GHA: yarn install
        GHA->>GHA: Run build-extension.sh<br/>(load .env → Vite build → zip)
        GHA->>GHA: Upload artifact
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over GHA: Upload Job
        GHA->>CLI: chrome-webstore-upload --trustedTesters
        CLI->>OAuth: Exchange refresh token for access token
        OAuth-->>CLI: Access token
        CLI->>CWS: Upload extension-dist.zip
        CWS-->>CLI: Upload success
        CLI-->>GHA: Done
    end

    GHA-->>Dev: Slack notification ✅
